snippet.title: Pathankot Terror Attack: NIA Suspects Pakistan's Hand in the Attack

localized.description:
Pathankot Terror Attack: NIA suspects Pakistan's hand in the attack. The National Investigation Agency (NIA) is now preparing to seek Pakistan’s help in identifying the six terrorists.
